# NOTE: assets/build/ MUST stay TRACKED. The wp.org release is published by
# Appsero (see appsero.json), which ships only git-tracked files. If assets/build
# is untracked the package ships with NO built blocks and the plugin breaks on
# activation (this caused the broken 2.2.5 + 2.2.6 releases). After any block/JS
# change: `npm run build` and commit assets/build/ with the source.
